                    <span>How to Change the World... is a fantastic book! I founded Projectchild.net and this book has provided me so so so much insight and excitement.  David, has out done himself, thank you Harry for gifting me this book! I will gift this book to all my social entrepreneurial friends.
<br />
<br />A must read for people who desire to change the world.
